        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does it work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We recommend using the mask <strong>1-2 times per week</strong> for best results.<strong><br/><br/>1️⃣  Prep</strong> – Cleanse your face & apply toner or serum.<br/><br/><strong>2️⃣  Apply</strong> – Remove the mask from the pouch & peel off the protective films.<br/><br/><strong>3️⃣  Wear</strong> – Place it on your face & leave for 1-2 hours (or until transparent).<br/><br/><strong>4️⃣  Remove</strong> – Gently take off the mask & pat in the extra essence.<br/><br/><strong>5️⃣  Glow</strong> – Enjoy hydrated, plump, and radiant skin!</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.</p><ul><li><strong>Collagen (25%)</strong><br/>Known for its brightening power, this multitasking vitamin refines pores, evens tone, and boosts skin clarity.<br/></li><li><strong>Niacinamide (25%)</strong> – Known for its brightening power, this multitasking vitamin refines pores, evens tone, and boosts skin clarity.<br/></li><li><strong>Hyaluronic Acid (20%)</strong> – A hydration powerhouse that deeply moisturizes and helps retain water for plump, dewy skin.<br/></li><li><strong>Vitamin E (Tocopherol, 20%)</strong> – A soothing antioxidant that protects the skin barrier and reduces visible signs of stress and aging.<br/></li><li><strong>Glycerin (10%)</strong> – A natural humectant that draws moisture into the skin, keeping it soft, supple, and nourished all day.<br/></li></ul><p>As with all skincare products, we highly recommend & urge you please patch test the mask serum on the skin of the arm or hand before using fully as some people are more sensitive than others or have allergic reactions to blends of ingredients.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Benefits",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Turn Back Time on Wrinkles:</strong> Smooth fine lines and wrinkles with every use, revealing youthful, glowing skin—no needles needed!</p><p><strong>Glow That Gets Noticed:</strong> Brighten dull, tired skin and rediscover a radiant, fresh-faced glow that turns heads.</p><p><strong>Simple to Use, Perfect Fit:</strong> Designed for effortless application and a snug fit, so you can mask your way to perfection—no mess, no fuss.</p><p><strong>Luxurious Ingredients You Can Trust:</strong> Packed with premium, skin-loving nutrients, free from harsh chemicals, for visible results you’ll love.</p><p><strong>All-in-One Beauty Boost:</strong> Say goodbye to dryness, puffiness, and uneven texture—one mask does it all for a smooth, hydrated complexion.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Should I wash after the mask?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>No, it is not necessary to wash your face after use. The remaining serum can be gently massaged into the skin for extra hydration.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! Designed to be gentle on the skin. Our mask does not strip moisture or dry out, making it ideal for all skin types.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We'll cover the cost of Tracked Shipping on all orders.<br/><br/><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 3-5 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p><p><strong>Returns:<br/></strong>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: Niforashop@gmail.com<em> </em></p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
